**APPROACH :**

* Convert the array into a 1D array ```v```.

* Reverse the array from index ```0``` to index ```v.size() - k - 1```.

* Then reverse the array from index ```v.size() - k``` to ```v.size() - 1```.

* Then reverse the whole array.

