For box we neeed simple bfs from box to target
for person we add a new function solve() which is a simple dfs function with seen set to check if a person can travel from his initial position to one position opposite from the direction where the box is moving. So directions is defined accordingly with 4 positions.Also from question its clear that after moving the box, position of the person becomes initial position of the box.
Before we porceed in solve() we make grid[i][j] as "#", since its given that a person cannot walk through box and make it "." after function returns.
If this function returns True, proceed further.
